graphql.query:
mutation ($payload:CciCreateChannelInput!)
{
	cciCreateChannel (payload:$payload)
	{
		id
		hash
		tenantCode
		systemName
		party
		component
		name
		flowHash
		flowParty
		flowReceiverParty
		flowComponent
		flowReceiverComponent
		flowInterfaceName
		flowInterfaceNamespace
		version
		adapterType
		direction
		transportProtocol
		messageProtocol
		adapterEngineName
		url
		username
		remoteHost
		remotePort
		directory
		fileSchema
		proxyHost
		proxyPort
		destination
		adapterStatus
		softwareComponentName
		responsibleUserAccountName
		lastChangeUserAccount
		lastChangedAt
		riInterfaceName
		riInterfaceNamespace
	}
}
